name: ITLibMediaItemVideoInfo
desc: This class encapsulates the video information of a video media item.

items.name: var videoWidth: Int
items.desc: The width of the video in pixels.

items.name: var videoHeight: Int
items.desc: The height of the video in pixels.

items.name: var series: String?
items.desc: The name of the corresponding TV series, if the media item is an episode in a TV series.

items.name: var sortSeries: String?
items.desc: The sorting name of the corresponding TV series, if the media item is an episode in a TV series.

items.name: var season: Int
items.desc: The corresponding TV season, if the media item is an episode of a TV series.

items.name: var isHD: Bool
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether the video is high-definition.

items.name: var episode: String?
items.desc: The name of the episode, if the media item is an episode of a TV series.

items.name: var episodeOrder: Int
items.desc: The numerical order of the episode, if the media item is an episode of a TV series.
